    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is the near future of 2019, and you're trapped in a dome with 18,736 mad robots on the outskirts of a Las Vegas themed resort, and with only twenty minutes until a bomb wipes everything out. Race across a small open world, activate powerful buffs, and grow strong enough to survive the next danger, and maybe even escape <i>(Ed. Escape is not possible at this point in time)</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321790/extras/5475bf1ddbf6aecb0de8576648b68c00.poster.avif?t=1738739348\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321790/extras/5475bf1ddbf6aecb0de8576648b68c00.webm?t=1738739348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321790/extras/5475bf1ddbf6aecb0de8576648b68c00.mp4?t=1738739348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore </strong>the world.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover Fountains to activate Buffs, Pylons to boost your character, and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race to locations to gain experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete Time-Trials to increase the experience you earn</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321790/extras/5b78489d31fbdf5a2a2d670bac314fcf.poster.avif?t=1738739348\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321790/extras/5b78489d31fbdf5a2a2d670bac314fcf.webm?t=1738739348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321790/extras/5b78489d31fbdf5a2a2d670bac314fcf.mp4?t=1738739348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explode</strong> the rustbuckets that have turned their attention to you.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilise a variety of unique weapons to Wreck those Wrobots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deal Damage to destroy their puny frames</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inflict Stun to weaken them, then ram into them to heal yourself</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilise Buffs to empower yourself and shape your run</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321790/extras/365e10d34b5309c677f734f56232034c.poster.avif?t=1738739348\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321790/extras/365e10d34b5309c677f734f56232034c.webm?t=1738739348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321790/extras/365e10d34b5309c677f734f56232034c.mp4?t=1738739348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Expire, </strong>and then try it all again.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock Achievements to unlock new Weapons, Buffs, and improve your car's stats</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discovered world features are added to your map permanently, letting you optimise your path through the world</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>If you haven't already, please consider checking out the Demo, it's a sizeable chunk of content, and will give you a very good idea if the game works for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
